      "content": "the proposal basically wants to hike corporate tax rates to 28% and increase the top marginal rate for high earners. it's basically a massive wealth grab that's gonna kill jobs and stifle growth. just write the script. don't be so formal, make it sound like a punchy, aggressive attack ad that makes them look out of touch and dangerous.",
